title: Will Prinsbot trade me a lamborghini?
description: It is possible that you may trade very profitable, but we that it is a quick rich is something we will not state.

title: Wich operation system do I need to have?
description: Prinsbot is web-based app that is availabe on desktop, mobile and tablets.

title: Will there be more exchanges available?
description: Yes, bittrex is for now the only exchange. But with more request for an exchange and an open API we will support it.

title: Can I sign up without registration?
description: No, It is not possible to purchase this software outside of our payment methods.Cryptoprins is a registered company and pays taxes on our sales.
